=== 數字與標點 ===
僧伽羅文有表示數字的特殊符號，一直使用到了19世紀初。現在被阿拉伯數字取代。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sundayobserver.lk/2004/09/19/fea29.html |title=Online edition of Sunday Observer - Business |publisher=Sundayobserver.lk |date= |accessdate=2008-09-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090207073829/http://sundayobserver.lk/2004/09/19/fea29.html |archivedate=2009-02-07 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://unicode.org/mail-arch/unicode-ml/y2006-m12/0127.html |title=Unicode Mail List Archive: Re: Sinhala numerals |publisher=Unicode.org |date= |accessdate=2008-09-21 |archive-date=2020-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200820110155/http://unicode.org/mail-arch/unicode-ml/y2006-m12/0127.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>以前用{{Unicode|෴}}作為表示完全停頓的標點符號。現在一般不再使用。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sinhala-online.com/sinhala-digits-number-page.html |title=Old Sinhala Numbers and Digits |publisher=Sinhala Online |author=Roland Russwurm |accessdate=2008-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080930221515/http://www.sinhala-online.com/sinhala-digits-number-page.html |archive-date=2008-09-30 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

== Unicode编码 ==
僧伽罗文在[[Unicode|Unicode]] 3.0及以后的版本获得支援，在U+0D80至U+0DFF的位置。
